<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h3 class="h2-heading-ss w-100">
      Material 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        structure and grain
      </span>
    </h3>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      The material structure and grain of a Balenciaga handbag are important indicators of its authenticity. Here are some things to look for:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-center">
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image article_column-image-border" src="{{ "balenciaga_material-structure-and-grain-1.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authentic Balenciaga bags have a Natural Grain">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Natural grain:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         The leather should be of high quality and have a natural grain, which is a hallmark of genuine Balenciaga bags.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_material-structure-and-grain-2.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authentic Balenciaga bags have the leather that is soft and supple to the touch">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Soft and supple texture:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The leather should be soft and supple to the touch, reflecting the premium materials used by Balenciaga.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_material-structure-and-grain-3.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authentic Balenciaga bags have No Visible Stitching or Glue Marks">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">No visible stitching or glue marks:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The bag should not have any visible stitching or glue marks, as these are signs of inferior craftsmanship.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-quarter block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image article_column-image-border" src="{{ "balenciaga_material-structure-and-grain-4.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authentic Balenciaga bags have Even Coloring and Consistent Texture">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Even coloring and consistent texture:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The leather should be evenly colored and have a consistent texture, indicating the meticulous attention to detail in authentic Balenciaga bags.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="body-text tac block-bottom-text w-100">
      By carefully examining the material structure and grain, you can ensure that you’re investing in a genuine Balenciaga handbag.
  </p>
</div>

